data.description: Take a look at this beautiful brick home on the east side! This home is move-in ready and would make the perfect home for a first time homebuyer or a growing family. With 3 bedrooms, 1 3/4 bath, you have plenty of room to grow in! As you walk in, you will see a beautiful living room with a gas fireplace perfect for the cooler Oklahoma weather! The kitchen and dining flow together with all new appliances and new kitchen sink. This home has a large 2 car garage with entry to the kitchen. All bedrooms are nice size with large closets. The primary bedroom has a walk-in closet and primary bath with walk-in shower. Once you step outside you will see a nice covered back patio perfect for entertaining with a privacy wooden fence.
